  "n: nat ==> dAbst(dBound(i), x, n) = dBound(i)"
  "n: nat ==> dAbst(dLam(M), x, n) = dLam(dAbst(M, x, succ(n)))"
  "n: nat ==> dAbst(dApp(A, B), x, n) =
                  dApp(dAbst(A, x, n), dAbst(B, x, n))"
